        <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-100 to-green-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Messaging Center</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 max-w-md mx-auto">
          The messaging center is currently under development. This feature will allow you to communicate with project stakeholders, team members, and receive important notifications.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            Real-time messaging
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            File attachments
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            Group conversations
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </EIULayout>
</Layout>
